th":{"items":"{{ CTX.devices_to_move }}","concurrency":"5"},"securitySchema":{"redact":{"input":[],"result":[]}},"action":{"id":"@@@action_ref3@@@"},"next":[{"do":["@@@workflow_task_id_ref3@@@"],"id":"@@@transition_id_ref5@@@","publish":[],"when":"{{ SUCCEEDED }}"}],"packOverrides":[]},{"id":"@@@workflow_task_id_ref7@@@","input":{"query_params":{"df":{"id":[],"role":[],"class":[],"group":null,"online":null,"status":null,"offline":null,"location":[],"not_role":[],"not_location":[],"organization":["{{ ORG.VARIABLES.ninja_org_id }}"],"created_after":null,"created_before":null,"not_organization":[]}}},"join":0,"retry":null,"mockInput":{"mock_result":{}},"isMocked":false,"humanSecondsSaved":0,"timeout":600,"transitionMode":"FOLLOW_ALL","publishResultAs":"all_devices","runAsOrgId":"","with":null,"securitySchema":{"redact":{"input":[],"result":[]}},"action":{"id":"@@@action_ref5@@@"},"next":[{"do":["@@@workflow_task_id_ref1@@@"],"id":"@@@transition_id_ref6@@@","publish":[],"when":"{{ SUCCEEDED }}"}],"packOverrides":[]}],"timeout":28800,"type":"STANDARD","varsSchema":{}},"nonfunctional_fields":{"description":"","name":"[BEZ - TASK] Ninja: Auto-Move Devices to Site with IP","notes[0].content":"## Goal\nCollect all NinjaRMM locations for the org and build a lookup map of `sitePublicIp -> locationId` using each location's custom fields.\n\n## Tasks\n1. **list_org_locations** - Calls the NinjaRMM API to list all locations for the org (keyed by `ORG.VARIABLES.ninja_org_id`). Publishes result as `CTX.org_locations`.\n2. **get_location_custom_fields** - Iterates over every location in parallel (concurrency: 5) and fetches its custom field values via the NinjaRMM API. Publishes result as `CTX.location_custom_fields`.\n3. **build_ip_to_location_map** - Iterates the paired `org_locations` / `location_custom_fields` lists and constructs a dict `{ sitePublicIp: locationId }` for every location that has a `sitePublicIp` custom field set. Publishes result as `CTX.ip_to_location_map`.\n\n## Key Inputs\n- `ORG.VARIABLES.ninja_org_id` - the NinjaRMM org ID for this tenant\n\n## Key Output\n- `CTX.ip_to_location_map` - dict used by Phase 2 to match devices to their correct site\n\n## Connects To\nPhase 2 (Device Collection & Filtering) consumes `CTX.ip_to_location_map`.","notes[0].metadata":{"x":-50,"y":70,"fill":"rgba(66, 158, 255, 0.05)","width":437,"height":716,"stroke":"rgba(66, 158, 255, 0.7)","padding":15,"task_ids":["019e47c0a3077330956e93c682094ff3","019e47c0bcbb717bb009b5e5ac893ab2","019e47f69d6a7c2fbba5c8215cef7fe5"],"fillEnabled":true,"positioning_mode":"task_container","requires_auto_position":false},"notes[0].title":"Phase 1: Location Data Collection & IP Map Build","notes[1].content":"## Goal\nRetrieve all devices for the org and identify which ones are assigned to the wrong site based on their public IP address.\n\n## Tasks\n1. **ninja_one_list_devices_detailed** - Fetches the full detailed device list for the org from NinjaRMM, filtered by `ninja_org_id`. Publishes result as `CTX.all_devices`.\n2. **build_devices_to_move** - Filters `CTX.all_devices` down to only devices that:\n   - Have a `publicIP` set\n   - Have a `publicIP` that exists in `CTX.ip_to_location_map`\n   - Are currently assigned to a `locationId` that does NOT match the mapped location for their IP\n   \n   Publishes the filtered list as `CTX.devices_to_move`.\n\n## Key Inputs\n- `CTX.ip_to_location_map` - from Phase 1\n- `CTX.all_devices` - full device list from NinjaRMM\n\n## Key Output\n- `CTX.devices_to_move` - list of device objects that need to be relocated\n\n## Connects To\nPhase 3 (Device Relocation) iterates over `CTX.devices_to_move`.","notes[1].metadata":{"x":-50,"y":838,"fill":"rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.05)","width":437,"height":452,"stroke":"rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.7)","padding":15,"task_ids":["c852ef568cb848b2a1caa719f469b44c","7defeae663ea4987ba3e9bb6a0094301"],"fillEnabled":true,"positioning_mode":"task_container","requires_auto_position":false},"notes[1].title":"Phase 2: Device Collection & Mismatch Filtering","notes[2].content":"## Goal\nMove each mismatched device to its correct NinjaRMM site by PATCHing its `locationId`, then terminate the workflow.\n\n## Tasks\n1. **move_device_to_site** - Iterates over `CTX.devices_to_move` in parallel (concurrency: 5). For each device, sends a `PATCH /device/{id}` request to NinjaRMM with the correct `locationId` looked up from `CTX.ip_to_location_map[item().publicIP]`.\n2. **done** - Terminal noop. Marks the workflow as complete with no further actions.\n\n## Key Inputs\n- `CTX.devices_to_move` - list of devices to relocate (from Phase 2)\n- `CTX.ip_to_location_map` - used to resolve the target `locationId` per device (from Phase 1)\n\n## Key Output\n- Each device's `locationId` is updated in NinjaRMM to match its public IP's site.\n\n## Notes\n- If `CTX.devices_to_move` is empty, the with-items loop completes immediately with no API calls made.\n- Concurrency is capped at 5 to avoid rate-limiting the NinjaRMM API.","notes[2].metadata":{"x":-50,"y":1366,"fill":"rgba(72, 199, 142, 0.05)","width":437,"height":452,"stroke":"rgba(72, 199, 142, 0.7)","padding":15,"task_ids":["019e48018ee575e0b33cc9fa638075a8","019e476ddce3798f9dc852450177ed9f"],"fillEnabled":true,"positioning_mode":"task_container","requires_auto_position":false},"notes[2].title":"Phase 3: Device Relocation & Completion","tasks[0].description":"Set a variable as an action","tasks[0].metadata":{"x":0,"y":1152},"tasks[0].name":"build_devices_to_move","tasks[0].next[0].from":null,"tasks[0].next[0].label":"","tasks[0].next[0].left":148,"tasks[0].next[0].orientation":"vertical","tasks[0].next[0].to":null,"tasks[0].next[0].top":1291,"tasks[1].description":"Build a dict mapping sitePublicIp -> location id, using the merged locations_with_ip list","tasks[1].metadata":{"x":0,"y":648},"tasks[1].name":"build_ip_to_location_map","tasks[1].next[0].from":null,"tasks[1].next[0].label":"","tasks[1].next[0].left":148,"tasks[1].next[0].orientation":"vertical","tasks[1].next[0].to":null,"tasks[1].next[0].top":763,"tasks[2].description":"Terminal noop — workflow complete","tasks[2].metadata":{"x":0,"y":1680},"tasks[2].name":"done","tasks[3].description":"For each location, fetch its custom field values. Runs in parallel across all locations.","tasks[3].metadata":{"x":0,"y":384},"tasks[3].name":"get_location_custom_fields","tasks[3].next[0].from":null,"tasks[3].next[0].label":"","tasks[3].next[0].left":148,"tasks[3].next[0].orientation":"vertical","tasks[3].next[0].to":null,"tasks[3].next[0].top":499,"tasks[4].description":"Get all locations for this org so we have their IDs to fetch custom fields per-location.","tasks[4].metadata":{"x":0,"y":120},"tasks[4].name":"list_org_locations","tasks[4].next[0].from":null,"tasks[4].next[0].label":"","tasks[4].next[0].left":148,"tasks[4].next[0].orientation":"vertical","tasks[4].next[0].to":null,"tasks[4].next[0].top":259,"tasks[5].description":"Move each device to the site whose sitePublicIp matches the device's publicIP","tasks[5].metadata":{"x":0,"y":1416},"tasks[5].name":"move_device_to_site","tasks[5].next[0].from":null,"tasks[5].next[0].label":"","tasks[5].next[0].left":148,"tasks[5].next[0].orientation":"vertical","tasks[5].next[0].to":null,"tasks[5].next[0].top":1531,"tasks[6].description":"Returns list of devices with additional information","tasks[6].metadata":{"x":0,"y":888},"tasks[6].name":"ninja_one_list_devices_detailed","tasks[6].next[0].from":null,"tasks[6].next[0].label":"","tasks[6].next[0].left":148,"tasks[6].next[0].orientation":"vertical","tasks[6].next[0].to":null,"tasks[6].next[0].top":1027},"references":{"transition_id_ref2":{"kind":"string","type":"transition_id","src_key_hash":"FainCCaDjNLoFgUXJTEoatKjSrwTPbKXHATEpzUMPiUu","content_hash":"429hpBBemz3CW1mTi92XyoYzd3a35bKDaZqMqXthT8vB","locations":["tasks[1].next[0].id"]},"action_ref5":{"kind":"string","type":"action","src_key_hash":"2uGL9MTWHbazWeZRtuTmAKhwAwPxK4F8953ALpzo7F5d","content_h